<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.2">
<l>eṉceyya tāmaraikkaṇ perumāṉārk keṉṟūtā</l>
<l>yeṉceyyu muraittakkā liṉakkuyilkā ṇīralirē</l>
<l>muṉceyta muḻuviṉaiyā ṟiruvaṭikkīḻk kuṟṟēval</l>
<l>muṉceyya muyalātē ṉakalvatuvō vitiyiṉamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When you speak as my envoy to my lord with red  lotus eyes,</l>
<l>what would it do [to you], pleasing Koels? Won’t you?</l>
<l>I who did not exert myself formerly in doing menial service under the sacred feet,</l>
<l>because of all the deeds done before, will that type of fate leave [me]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
